Title: S5 Ep. 225 Jack Henkel
Description:
I have known Jack Henkel for about 5 years when he was visited StarterStudio (an accelerator) and was working with UCF I-Corps and .  He works with the Florida High Tech Corridor's Cenfluence Program as a Sr. Cluster Manager.  Jack is the definition of a #servantleader, he is one of those individuals that is behind the scenes and I am so glad to share his interview with our listeners. Tune in to hear the five words that he shares that will give you insight to who he is and his thoughts about what the future of work and innovation will look like. Hint, flying cars was one of our topics.
